                  <summary>Asmat prayers for conception and against hemorrhage, (accordion-fold book)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1" to="14" facs="001">Fols 1–14</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer">Asmat prayers for conception and against hemorrhage</title>
